item.title: 3 Hour Tour de Columbus E-Bike Tour
item.description:
Experience the best of Columbus up close with our unforgettable e-bike tours! This thrilling 3-hour adventure takes you through the city’s iconic landmarks, scenic parks, and vibrant neighborhoods. We will also cruise on the renowned Olentangy Trail. From the historic streets of downtown to the energetic vibe of Ohio State University, you’ll discover the unique character and charm of Columbus’ most beloved areas.
Begin with an orientation to get familiar and comfortable with your e-bike. Then, set off on a guided tour that runs on bike paths and protected bike lanes most of the ride, keeping a strong adherence to comfort and safety.
Ride on state-of-the-art e-bikes, featuring front and rear shocks, fat tires for a smooth ride, and 1,000 watt motors to power your ride up to 28 mph. Cruise from the bustling Short North Arts District to the scenic Scioto Mile and hidden gems in German Village.
All riders must arrive 20 minutes prior to tour start time.

image.alt: 3 Hour Tour de Columbus E-Bike Tour

item.title: 3.5 Hour Self-Guided/Guided Olentangy Trail E-Bike Adventure
item.description:
Embark on an extraordinary e-bike adventure designed for nature enthusiasts. This journey along the renowned Olentangy Trail, one of Columbus’ most popular and scenic paths, offers a seamless blend of natural beauty, recreational opportunities, and cultural landmarks. Beginning in downtown Columbus, you’ll set out on an 18-mile trek north, traveling through lush, winding wooded trails and passing through picturesque parks teeming with vibrant trees, native plants, and diverse wildlife.
As this is a dedicated bike trail, there’s no need to navigate busy traffic roads, ensuring a peaceful and immersive experience. Our ride culminates at Worthington Hills Park, where you can pause at the Rusty Bucket, giving you the chance to enjoy a refreshing drink or snack. After a short break, you’ll journey back to downtown Columbus, completing a one-of-a-kind excursion. No other city e-bike can take you further than our bikes can!
Tour guides available upon request. Call/email us for pricing.

image.alt: 3.5 Hour Self-Guided/Guided Olentangy Trail E-Bike Adventure
